\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The tension we all struggle with is as Christians we have been told that 
\f0\b \cf4 a good Christian is someone follows the teachings of Jesus
\f1\b0 \cf0 \'85and that works great\'85in a generic form but isn\'92t so awesome when you break it down and start to look closer.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The Bible doesn\'92t tell you\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Who to marry \'96 tells you what type of woman but not who\
