{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}If you should have more kids or any at all\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Which job to take and where\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Where to live\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Most of the decisions you make on a daily basis you can\'92t find answers for specifically in the Bible\'85all you have are generic principles\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Which\'85and this is where we are going\'85is why you\'92ve made some of the biggest mistakes of your life!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Because, while there was a verse for or against your biggest mistake, there were none for all the decisions that lead up to your mistakes.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Examples here:\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}If your grid for making decisions is \'96 There\'92s not a verse against it, therefore God must be ok with it!  You will live a very frustrated and confused life.\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}No verse against messaging your old boyfriend on Facebook!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}No verse for Credit cards \'96 It\'92s 0% with cash back\'85so technically I\'92m making money on this deal here\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf3 Transition:  Luckily God, knowing how we think because he created us, he put some principles in scripture to help us through situations like this and that is what this series is built around.  \
