{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Paul in this book we\'92re going to look at goes through a lot of different specific issues to make sure they do what God wants them to do.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}But at some point Paul realizes what you\'92ve realized before that it doesn\'92t really cover everything.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}And if your only grid in life is to just what the Bible details out then I promise you, you\'92re going to get yourself into trouble.\
